# Contact → Scan page (main CTA)
/contact /scan 301

# WWW to non-WWW (or vice versa - pick one)
https://goldsmithgrowth.com/* https://www.goldsmithgrowth.com/:splat 301

# Old HTTP to HTTPS
http://* https://:splat 301